      "type": "heading",
      "title": "Project Statement"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Smart Manufacturing Ltd. manufactures industrial motors and electrical equipment for customers across India. Daily production exceeds 800 customer orders. Transportation planning is partially automated, but warehouse loading bottlenecks, vehicle shortages and urgent customer requests frequently delay deliveries. Management wants SAP TM to improve transportation planning while coordinating efficiently with warehouse operations."
    },
